{"id":98359,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/1-假设人类所有的知识，就是一个圆。圆的内部代/","date":"2010-08-14T09:45:49Z","modified":"2010-08-14T09:45:49Z","title":"1. 假设人类所有的知识，就是一个圆。圆的内部代表已知，圆的外部代表未知。 2&#8230;.","content":"<p><p>来自: <a href=\"http://www.feedzshare.com/b/125/2\">科学松鼠会 &#8211; FeedzShare</a>  <br />\n<br />发布时间:2010年08月13日,  已有 4 人推荐 </p>\n<hr>\n<div>\n<p>1.</p>\n<p>假设人类所有的知识，就是一个圆。圆的内部代表已知，圆的外部代表未知。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0018.jpg\"><img title=\"clip_image001[8]\" src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0018_thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"clip_image001[8]\" width=\"644\" height=\"484\" /></a></p>\n<p>2.</p>\n<p>读完小学，你有了一些最基本的知识。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0028.jpg\"><img title=\"clip_image002[8]\" src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0028_thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"clip_image002[8]\" width=\"644\" height=\"484\" /></a></p>\n<p>3.</p>\n<p>读完中学，你的知识又多了一点。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0038.jpg\"><img title=\"clip_image003[8]\" src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0038_thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"clip_image003[8]\" width=\"644\" height=\"484\" /></a></p>\n<p>4.</p>\n<p>读完本科，你不仅有了更多的知识，而且还有了一个专业方向。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0048.jpg\"><img title=\"clip_image004[8]\" src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0048_thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"clip_image004[8]\" width=\"644\" height=\"484\" /></a></p>\n<p>5.</p>\n<p>读完硕士，你在专业上又前进了一大步。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0058.jpg\"><img title=\"clip_image005[8]\" src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0058_thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"clip_image005[8]\" width=\"644\" height=\"484\" /></a></p>\n<p>6.</p>\n<p>进入博士生阶段，你大量阅读文献，接触到本专业的最前沿。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0068.jpg\"><img title=\"clip_image006[8]\" src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0068_thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"clip_image006[8]\" width=\"644\" height=\"484\" /></a></p>\n<p>7.</p>\n<p>你选择边界上的一个点，也就是一个非常专门的问题，作为自己的主攻方向。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0078.jpg\"><img title=\"clip_image007[8]\" src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0078_thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"clip_image007[8]\" width=\"644\" height=\"484\" /></a></p>\n<p>8.</p>\n<p>你在这个点上苦苦思索，也许需要好几年。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0088.jpg\"><img title=\"clip_image008[8]\" src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0088_thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"clip_image008[8]\" width=\"644\" height=\"484\" /></a></p>\n<p>9.</p>\n<p>终于有一天，你突破了这个点。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0098.jpg\"><img title=\"clip_image009[8]\" src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0098_thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"clip_image009[8]\" width=\"644\" height=\"484\" /></a></p>\n<p>10.</p>\n<p>你把人类的知识向前推进了一步，这时你就成为博士了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0108.jpg\"><img title=\"clip_image010[8]\" src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0108_thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"clip_image010[8]\" width=\"644\" height=\"484\" /></a></p>\n<p>11.</p>\n<p>现在你就是最前沿，其他人都在你身后。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0118.jpg\"><img title=\"clip_image011[8]\" src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0118_thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"clip_image011[8]\" width=\"644\" height=\"484\" /></a></p>\n<p>12.</p>\n<p>但是，不要陶醉在这个点上，不要把整张图的样子忘了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0128.jpg\"><img title=\"clip_image012[8]\" src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/clip_image0128_thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"clip_image012[8]\" width=\"644\" height=\"484\" /></a></p>\n<p>继续努力向前推进吧！</p>\n<p>（完）</p>\n<p>本文地址（转载请注明出处）： 复制</p>\n<p>收藏、分享这篇文章：<br />\n<a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" title=\"收藏到豆瓣\"><img src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/plugins/share-this/douban.gif\" alt=\"豆瓣\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" title=\"分享到新浪微博\"><img src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/plugins/share-this/sina-t.jpg\" alt=\"新浪微博\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" title=\"分享到人人\"><img src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/plugins/share-this/renren.gif\" alt=\"人人网\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kaixin001.com/repaste/share.php?rtitle=%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E6%9D%BE%E9%BC%A0%E4%BC%9A%EF%BC%9A&#038;rurl=http://songshuhui.net/archives/41442.html&#038;rcontent=http://songshuhui.net/archives/41442.html\" title=\"转贴到开心网\"><img src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/plugins/share-this/kaixin.gif\" alt=\"开心网\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sns.qzone.qq.com/cgi-bin/qzshare/cgi_qzshare_onekey?url=http://songshuhui.net/archives/41442.html\" title=\"分享到QQ Zone\"><img src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/ico_Qzone.gif\" alt=\"QQ空间\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" title=\"收藏到qq书签\"><img src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/plugins/share-this/qqbookmark.gif\" alt=\"qq书签\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" title=\"分享到人民微博\"><img src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/plugins/share-this/people.jpg\" alt=\"人民微博\" width=\"16\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" title=\"GOOGLE书签\"><img src=\"http://songshuhui.net/wp-content/plugins/share-this/google_bmarks.gif\" alt=\"GOOGLE书签\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.myspace.cn/Modules/PostTo/Pages/Default.aspx?t=%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E6%9D%BE%E9%BC%A0%E4%BC%9A%EF%BC%9A&#038;u=http://songshuhui.net/archives/41442.html\" title=\"分享到Mys